{"id":15006,"date":"2023-02-24T11:10:25","date_gmt":"2023-02-24T11:10:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/?page_id=15006"},"modified":"2024-03-06T11:24:31","modified_gmt":"2024-03-06T11:24:31","slug":"10years","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/10years\/","title":{"rendered":"10 Year Anniversary"},"content":{"rendered":"\n\n<!-- hero -->\n<section class=\"subpage-hero-section\" style=\"background: url('https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/10-Year-Anniversary-Main-Logo-Lower-2.png') center center no-repeat; background-size:cover;background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.4); background-blend-mode: overlay;\">\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-10 offset-lg-1\">\n               <h1 data-aos=\"fade-up\" class=\"subpage-hero-h\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF\">10 Year Anniversary<\/h1>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"title-section title-same-line\">\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-10 offset-lg-1\">\n                <h2 data-aos=\"fade-up\" class=\"section-h text-center cd-headline loading-bar bold pink\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"pink\" > <\/p> \n                    <span class=\"cd-words-wrapper blue\">\n                                                \n                    <\/span><\/h2>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"changable-section process pt-0\">\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-3 offset-lg-1 d-flex align-items-start justify-content-center flex-column\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n                <h2 class=\"section-h\">10 Years Pioneering Education<\/h1>\n                <p class=\"section-p\">Halcyon London International School opened its doors to students for the first time on 2 September 2013. This September, 2023, our School will be 10 years old &#8211; a significant milestone for everyone in the Halcyon community.<br><br>Through the school year 2023\/24 we will celebrate our success together: our exceptional IB education; our innovative, student-centred, wellbeing programme; and our focus on innovation in learning. <br><br>\r\nWe are the only not-for-profit IB school in central London. Students enjoy academic success because they feel valued, confident and secure.\r\n<\/p>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"col-lg-7 text-right mission-image blue-frame p-0\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/VB21_HALCYON_D3_512p-2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <\/section>\n\n\n\n\n<!-- image section -->\n<section class=\"image-section\">\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-4 offset-lg-1\">\n                <h2 class=\"section-h after blue\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">A message from Co-Founder Rita Halbright<\/h2>\n                <p class=\"section-p\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">Early on in the discussions that were to become Halcyon, co-founders Achim, Julie, Pamela and I were inspired by a number of overlapping visions of why we needed to create Halcyon. <br><br> As we reflect on our first ten years, I\u2019d like to share with you what led me on this journey which, frankly, has become a life-defining achievement for me. <br><br> I hope it has been an equally life-affirming experience for those who have become involved with Halcyon; as student, staff, parent or otherwise.<\/p>\n                <div class=\"d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between flex-wrap\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n                    <span class=\"signature\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\" alt=\"\" \/><\/span>\n                    <a class=\"button small blue-outline\" href=\"h